{"tid":1068623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬時亨：保留追究新信號系統承辦商權利","createTime":"2019-03-19T10:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T11:33:33.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"db750fca4799a4c9f0c1fcd2af68cdc0616a3f7c","tid":1068623,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T10:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190319/s00001/d78526c2b43eef4a2ac3dc9142aa97fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190319%2Fs00001%2Fd78526c2b43eef4a2ac3dc9142aa97fc.jpg&h=ed8ac1da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵兩列列車昨凌晨測試新信號系統期間，在中環站及金鐘站之間的「渡線」相撞。港鐵主席馬時亨傍晚會見傳媒，表示會保留追究新信號系統承辦商的權利。<br />\n<br />\n車務總監劉天成則表示，爭取在今晚收車後，將偏離路軌的列車頭卡放回軌道，嘗試可否駛離正線，未有正面回應何時可重開荃灣線中環來往金鐘的服務。"},{"pid":"a15fb71b8dba9743421ea8802c0e71c98cb64b16","tid":1068623,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T10:57:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190319/s00001/1552992369762/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190319%2Fs00001%2F1552992369762%2F&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=ff28be2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190319%2Fs00001%2F1552992369762%2F&h=b3c24878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190319/s00001/1552992369762/</a>"},{"pid":"dd20b010c5cc70ed311b9aa4cbf973f9d8977a21","tid":1068623,"uid":20933,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T10:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7t1ZXus.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7t1ZXus.png&h=bbc06d3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"927cdc1d5e264fbe1a0d0b0eb788ba30ce5746dd","tid":1068623,"uid":997,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:00:37.000Z"